Open https://github.com/Shopify/kubeaudit/release on your browser.
Copy link of latest version
Use wget to download
Extract the tar file
  tar -xvzf kubeaudit_linux_amd64.tar.gz # edit with the correct version
# move the kubeaudit to the user local bin directory
   sudo mv kubeaudit /usr/local/bin
# To scan the cluster, run
     kubeaudit all  
